      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON RULER (8) jumped wide and had a clear run last start, leading all the way to score (34.67) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 601m. Has a strong record from box 8, including four wins. Hard to fault his form and makes plenty of appeal again. CLEARY MAGIC (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (35.42) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Should be in this for a long way. LICORICE MONELLI (1) turned in a solid run last start over 520m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (30.16). Will give the top chances plenty to think about. HUM BUG MONELLI (7) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
